name: Dewey Does 'Catch Them If You Can' Game
blurb: Dewey Does 110% Challenge, catch as many pieces of sports equipment, fitness equipment and fruits and veggies with Dewey Does.

rewards.reward: Be a Dewey Does 110% Supporter.  Receive new game level updates and promotional giveaway notices.  Receive a personal 110% appreciation email from the Dewey Does Team.

Write your own Sports, Fitness, Health, & Wellness trivia question to be included in the DD game and posted on DeweyDoes.com next to your name.  All relevant questions are posted and top 110 questions for 2012 receive FREE Dewey Does car window decal.  Voted on by Dewey Does Fans.  We love brand based and youth type questions. Must provide answer with question.

All of the above plus receive a sporty Dewey Does logo bumper magnet. The Dewey Does 110% logo bumper magnet can be proudly displayed on your car bumper or home refrigerator. A symbol for youth sports & activities.  Kids view it as cool and athletic. Includes updates of new levels with free links to download. Please share with friends; 5000 logo bumper magnets in 25 days.

In addition to the previous, receive a DVD of the Dewey Does 4 President animation with the full downloadable Dewey Does Sports song, playing in the beginning and end of video, for all to sing along. This is a perfect gift item for a child's birthday or holiday. Please include an additional $15 for international shipping.

In addition to all above receive a 3 book set of Dewey Does' 'Heroes Start as 110% Kids'. Book one is distributed by Scholastic Inc. in schools throughout the U.S. and overseas. Kids love them and you will too. Midwest Book Review says, "First Day will prove to be a popular addition and will leave young readers looking eagerly toward the next Dewey Does adventure!" Please include an additional $15 for international shipping.

All of the above plus be the first to receive the new signature trademark Dewey Does apparel. Look cool and athletic, pick one of the four available colors that brightly displays the hot Dewey Does logo. Available in youth and adult sizes as well as female cuts. ONLY in heather gray and white for now. Please include an additional $4 for sizes 3x and 4x adult and an additional $20 for international shipping.  PLUS, be the first to know about all new updates on future Dewey Does games and the opportunity to receive them for FREE.

All of the above plus receive all four Dewey Does trademark logo colors for the family or for yourself. ONLY in heather gray and white for now. Please include an additional $20 for international shipping. (Free collectable DD All Sport bobble head only during this KickStarter campaign - first 110 pledges for all 4 tee shirt designs). Designed from the Dewey Does All Sport logo on the game cover. Tees delivered in July 2012 and DD bobble head in November 2012.

Receive all above plus the character you create will be placed in advertising campaigns to promote the Dewey Does 'Catch Them If You Can' game. You will receive recognition and honors for your specific character. Ads with your character will appear on the internet and in print. Includes one tee shirt from Reward #7. TOP 10 CHARACTERS ARE MADE INTO A BOBBLE HEAD OR FIGURINE AS A GIFT TO YOU.  Voted on by Dewey Does Fans for 2012.  (Does not include Kickstarter bobble head campaign.)

Receive all above plus your own sports equipment character placed in the Dewey Does \u2018Catch Them If You Can\u2019 game level 4 first Edition. Hundreds of thousands, maybe even millions of Dewey Does fans trying to catch your personally designed character. You will be part of the history of the Dewey Does brand. In addition, your copy of the Dewey Does \u2018Heroes Start as 110% Kids! book series will be personally signed by the author, John Cooper and the creator of Dewey Does, Thomas Kinslow. Includes one tee shirt from Reward #7. (Does not include Kickstarter bobble head campaign.)
